<ul>
<li>PPC returns <a href="https://economicimpact.google.com/methodology/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">$2 for every $1 spent</a>‚Äîresulting in a 200% ROI.</li>
<li>Paid ad channels with the highest reported ROI rate are <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/marketing-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook Ads and Google Ads</a>.</li>
<li><a href="https://backlinko.com/seo-stats" target="_blank" rel="noopener">49%</a> of businesses say that organic search brings them the best <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/marketing-roi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marketing ROI</a>.</li>
