<li>Small businesses claim that email marketing is the marketing channel that brings them the <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/marketing-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noopener">highest return on investment</a>.</li>
<li>Over <a href="https://www.impression.co.uk/blog/marketing-census-2021/">20%</a> of businesses say that the number of leads generated is the primary factor they base the success of their <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/marketing-channels/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marketing channels</a>.</li>
