<li>Less than <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/marketing-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noopener">20%</a> of marketers use landing page A/B tests to improve conversion rates. Not sure what to test? Get some inspiration from these <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/03/08/landing-page-examples">landing page examples.</a></li>
<li>About <a href="https://www.smallbizgenius.net/by-the-numbers/seo-statistics/#gref" target="_blank" rel="noopener">70% to 80%</a> of people completely ignore paid digital ads. Be sure yours stand out with<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2017/01/12/how-to-write-great-advertising-copy"> compelling ad copy</a> that speaks to your <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2014/09/18/beginners-guide-to-target-markets">target market.</a></li>
