<li><a href="https://www.searchenginejournal.com/seo-guide/seo-statistics/#close">Half </a>of all browser-based searches on Google end with no clicks. To combat this, try <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/01/13/best-words-and-phrases-for-marketing">marketing with emotion </a>in your content to turn uninterested searchers into click-happy visitors.</li>
